# --- CapacityOS standard repo .gitignore ---

# Scratch / working state only: temporary files, caches, intermediate renders.
# (Durable artifacts do NOT go here -- they go to the mirrored JB/library/.
#  Secrets/regulated docs do NOT go here -- they go to the secure vault.
#  See CapacityOS/system/meta/architecture/artifact-information-architecture.md.)
_local/

# Video binaries do not belong in git. Durable video is a class-2 artifact ->
# JB/library/repos/{private,public}/<repo>/ (mirrored). _local is scratch only.
*.mp4
*.mov
*.avi
*.webm
*.mkv

# OS / editor junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*~
*.tmp
